Re-Enter Trades After Exit

This feature will allow you to automatically re-enter a trade after specified exit conditions are triggered (stop loss, short tested, etc). You can optionally add a delay before re-entry, as well as a minimum and maximum time of day (most useful for 0 DTE). * Note: the re-entered trade will use the same entry criteria (deltas, widths, DTEs, entry conditions) as the original trade.

